{
  "stem": "13690.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The past experience that I had with the people that I live-- and I do consider myself that I was born in Poland, that I'm a Jew born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could not deny, and neither do I want to deny it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do say it, that the guilt that the Polish people have-- and they should come up, and they will eventually come up-- is because they did not have the education.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not educated to understand to be equal with all their citizens of their country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other words, I do say, if the Polish people would had a better education, there would not be that much hatred.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The great part of it that the Polish people had-- and I want to have it on record-- the only education that the Polish people had is to go to church and to listen what the Church is saying.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Therefore, the Church has a big part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't blame the Poles, and don't blame anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Blame the Church for the unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are blessed now with a great pope which happens to be born in Poland, the country of my ancestors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I was expecting-- he's doing a great job, fantastic job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He's the only pope that history could show that is moving, is, is movable, doing things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's a doer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In gratitude, we always remember them, and we'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We try to support them till this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Placzek died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I came back after 40 years to Poland, the first thing what I did, I came to town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the cemetery to pay the respect to the-- Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Placzek.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
